{"tid":610043,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］打到男朋友流血","createTime":"2018-03-29T14:26:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T21:52:26.000Z","uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f8a6740192d4a63c14e2c74b3950380842f1f0b1","tid":610043,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T14:26:14.000Z","msg":"啱啱好頹好憎自己所以不斷摑自己摑到塊面腫曬<br />\n咬自己捏自己 成隻手瘀曬流曬血 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住男朋友咁啱返到黎見到我咁<br />\n佢即刻衝過黎攬住我叫我唔好咁樣做<br />\n要打就打佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為我癲曬所以就失曬控咁打佢咬佢佢完全無反抗 佢話：<br />\n「如果可以選擇嘅話我願意為你承受任何痛楚黎換你嘅快樂㗎傻妹」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果.....<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n我發現自己根本就無男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae9fd98d904ae461b176cf9dcfe06ab9e774964","tid":610043,"uid":179503,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T14:27:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4641a441cdcc030d7a9c3db71e5d607c98bf9398","tid":610043,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T14:27:50.000Z","msg":"Haha"},{"pid":"faebb6b8969c995b951f04a3f553e3d56dbfc278","tid":610043,"uid":89514,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T14:30:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b4dfd40289c45f3a2f9b6fd13375c13d1b35808","tid":610043,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"faebb6b8969c995b951f04a3f553e3d56dbfc278","tid":610043,"uid